Longevities for 133 Canidae species

df_longevities_canidae.Rd

Data frame containing Time of Speciation (TS) and Time of Extinction (TE) for 133 Canidae species

Usage

df_longevities_canidae

Format

A data frame object with 133 rows and 3 columns:

species

Species names

TS

Time of Speciation

TE

Time of Extinction

Source

https://academic.oup.com/evolut/article/79/9/1835/8140865#535027902
